703252f-a.text:
Bleecker Street, at the N.E. corner of Wilson Ave. (Hamburg Ave.) showing a building partially demolished which was known as the Palm Garden, (a beer garden).  The wall at the extreme right, is part of the North American Brewing Co.
May 1925.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
